说，韩国在野党 5 日凌晨向国会全体会议报告针对总统尹锡悦的弹劾动议案。国会将在 6 日至 7 日进行表决。 尹锡悦 3 日晚在首尔龙山总统府发表紧急谈话，发布紧急戒严令，6 小时后宣布解除戒严。韩国多个在野党 4 日下午就此向国会发起对总统的弹劾动议案。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-26fabbe5350689b5080876e0a72d9641_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "123 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/6099505323"}}, "attached_info": "CkAItbbKoou914JaEAMaCTExMjE5Njc0OCCElcm6BjAAOENABXIKNjA5OTUwNTMyM3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1733458449.647255", "card_id": "Q_576011192", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 44}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《骆驼祥子》为什么三次买车以后人就颓了？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "刚又重看了一遍儿骆驼祥子，前前后后他也不过花了 10 年时间，三次起落，为什么会变得颓废？现在也不过才 30 岁啊，完全可以试试再买一辆新车，100 大洋攒三年，总比 1000 大洋 30 年容易多了，也不会烂尾"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c1dcc7de48b3055bc8b6158648a6b01b_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "96 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/576011192"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4ItbbKoou914JaEAMaCDkwMjg0MDUwIK+uw50GMAA4RUAGcgk1NzYwMTExOTJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1733458449.647637", "card_id": "Q_6013422513", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2025 世俱杯抽签结果出炉，迈阿密国际上签，曼城对阵尤文，你对改